Changes from Version 1.0.1.4 to 1.0.2
* added fortran macros to adapt the package for LAPACKII
* changed versioning to three-component (as per CRAN requirements)
* Michal Burdukiewicz <michalburdukiewicz@gmail.com> becomes a new maintainer of the package. Thanks to 
Seyed Morteza Najibi for maintaining and Patrick O. Perry for developing the package.
